
1: Download xampp from  apachefriends.org

2: Opwn the apps/file/package folder.

3: sudo chmod 755 xampp-linux-x64-8.2.12-0-installer.run

4: sudo ./xampp-linux-x64-8.2.12-0-installer.run

5: click forward, donot select xampp core files , select xampp developer files

6: xampp will be install to /opt/lampp

7: START :
	sudo /opt/lampp/lampp start
	
8: STOP :
	sudo /opt/lampp/lampp stop

9: RESTART :
	sudo /opt/lampp/lampp restart
	
10: Uninstall :
	
	
	
browser: localhost/phpmyadmin
